This is a big data project for loan risk prediction. 
Data collection:
The dataset is taken from Kaggle, and the subject itâ€™s represented by the accepted loans from 2007 to 2018 in the USA, that contains detailed information and a variety of attributes that provide a view of the lending area during the mentioned period.
Here you will find:
-An in-depth EDA
-Statistical analysis
-Feature engineering
-Data visualization
-Dimensionality reduction using: PCA and LDA
-ML techniques: Logistic Regression, Random Forest,Support Vector Machine, GBM
